description: Latest version of a mod that introduces several significant new player movement mechanics to Quake, including trampolines, climbable wiremeshes and lighthooks (similar to grapple hooks). Includes all the original maps from version 1.1 and this jam, plus five completely new maps.
notes: This file was repackaged for Quake Injector compatibility.
May require a source port with increased limits / BSP2 support.
